                            <comment id="13991909" author="yukim" created="Wed, 7 May 2014 15:29:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Isn&apos;t it better to use &lt;a href=&quot;http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/lang/Boolean.html#parseBoolean%28java.lang.String%29&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Boolean.parseBoolean&lt;/a&gt;?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13991919" author="brandon.williams" created="Wed, 7 May 2014 15:37:15 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Isn&apos;t it better to use Boolean.parseBoolean?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
