                            <comment id="13992020" author="brandon.williams" created="Wed, 7 May 2014 17:23:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1.  Looks like 1.2 needs this as well.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13992544" author="krummas" created="Thu, 8 May 2014 06:22:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;committed&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think we are good in 1.2, we do:&lt;br/&gt;
minCompactionThreshold.reset();&lt;br/&gt;
maxCompactionThreshold.reset();&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;in enableAutocompaction(), which resets it to the original value&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
